To assess alterations in sustained attention we conducted an rm-ANOVA on the composite RT on the two sustained attention tasks with three time points (baseline, 1-week, 1-month) and the between-subjects factor of tACS group (theta, control). The results revealed a main effect of time (F1.31,23.56 = 17.34, p < 0.001, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
