				\begin{document}$$\upeta _{{\text{p}}}^{{2}}$$\end{document}ηp2 = 0.49), such that performance improved (reduced RT) following a week of tACS + CCT (Table 2). There was no between-subjects effect of group (F1,18 = 2.50, p = 0.131, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
