				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\upeta _{{\text{p}}}^{{2}}$$\end{document}ηp2 = 0.12). Importantly, there was a significant time × group interaction (F1.31,23.56 = 6.25, p = 0.014, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
