				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\upeta _{{\text{p}}}^{{2}}$$\end{document}ηp2) and with Cohen’s d for independent samples t-tests. Post-hoc comparisons within rm-ANOVAs were Bonferroni-corrected.
